Y-6DS","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":25570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/07\/light-sleep-not-nullify-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":25536,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Light sleep does not invalidate ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would sleep lightly and then perform prayer without renewing ablution. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 376 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe scholars disagreed regarding ablution for one who slept. The majority\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":309,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/04\/the-virtue-of-ablution-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":25536,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Ablution is radiance on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 4, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, my nation will be called on the Day of Resurrection as brightly radiant from the traces of ablution. Whoever among you is able to extend his radiance, let him do so.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 136, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/31\/miracle-prophet-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":25536,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet&#8217;s miracle of providing water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 31, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during the afternoon prayer and people were asking for water to perform ablution, but they could not find it. Some water was brought to the Prophet and he placed his hand in the vessel\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25581,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/07\/wudu-ablution-hadath-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25536,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Ablution required before prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer is not accepted from one in a state of minor impurity until he renews ablution.\u201d A man from Hadhramaut said, \u201cAbu Huraira, what is minor impurity?\u201d Abu Huraira said, \u201cIt is passing wind or gas.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/forgives-between-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25536,"position":4},